TITLE: Kalki Avatar | Grp Member Trishla Divine Experience With Maa Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta Ji
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bpfaNvEwmgU
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Trishla shares her experience of connecting with Maa Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta through social media long before joining the WhatsApp group. She had always felt a strong positivity and positive energy from Maa and wanted to meet her and connect with her. When she finally got the opportunity to join the group, she was able to know Maa more closely and understand her words, thoughts, and experiences more deeply, finding meaningful messages in everything.

Since connecting, Trishla has become more spiritual and closer to spirituality. Her awareness has significantly increased -- she now understands the reasons behind things that happen. The group discussions connect to her personal life in meaningful ways. She feels Maa's divine blessings and protective energy constantly, as if she has come under Maa's umbrella of protection. She describes feeling happier, more positive, and more confident since joining. She considers Maa's entry into her life as a divine blessing.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Was following Maa on social media for a long time before joining the group
- Always felt strong positive energy from Maa even before personal connection
- Experienced significant increase in awareness and understanding of life's reasons
- Every group discussion topic connects to her personal life in meaningful ways
- Feels under Maa's protective umbrella (chhatra-chhaaya) with constant divine blessings

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: Divine Experience

